<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[418, 165, 536, 183]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 196, 234, 213]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 225, 384, 244]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\),

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[396, 245, 561, 280]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}.\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 312, 222, 329]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[225, 336, 727, 371]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1} b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2} b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r} b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 383, 500, 415]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\).

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[384, 482, 569, 500]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 515, 154, 530]]<|/det|>
Identities

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[400, 543, 551, 562]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[400, 568, 551, 587]]<|/det|>
\[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[395, 593, 559, 612]]<|/det|>
\[\csc^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 642, 235, 658]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[384, 664, 568, 694]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[381, 715, 571, 735]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc \cos A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[418, 743, 534, 771]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc \sin A\]
